OL,3,COlympics: Matt Richards makes history
OL,4,Cin freestyle relay gold win
OL,6,FWelsh swimmer Matt Richards' father
OL,7,Fhas said it was a "privilege" to watch
OL,8,Fhis son make Olympic "history" on
OL,9,FTuesday (30 July).
OL,11,FThe 21-year-old, who was born in
OL,12,FEngland but swims for Wales, swam as
OL,13,Fpart of the men's 4200 metres
OL,14,Ffreestyle relay team, winning and
OL,15,Fretaining the gold medal.
OL,17,FThe same four-man team, consisting of
OL,18,FJames Guy, Tom Dean, Matt Richards and
OL,19,FDuncan Scott had previously won
OL,20,FOlympic gold in the relay at the Tokyo
OL,21,F2020 games.
