OL,3,COlympics: Matt Richards makes history
OL,4,Cin freestyle relay gold win
OL,6,FThe quartet stood atop the podium
OL,7,Fafter edging out the United States by
OL,8,F1.35 seconds.
OL,10,FSimon Richards from Cardiff was in
OL,11,FParis watching his son Matt's gold
OL,12,Fmedal finish.
OL,14,FThe proud father had decorated his
OL,15,Fhouse in anticipation of the 2024
OL,16,FOlympics and was "belting out God Save
OL,17,Fthe King" following his son's history-
OL,18,Fmaking win.
