OL,3,COlympics: Matt Richards makes history
OL,4,Cin freestyle relay gold win
OL,6,FThis is the first time a swimming team
OL,7,Fhas defended an Olympic relay title
OL,8,Fwith the same four team members.
OL,10,FHe said: "Never in Olympic history
OL,11,Fhave four individuals ever retained
OL,12,FOlympic gold in a swimming relay.
OL,14,F"Countries have done it, but never the
OL,15,Fsame four swimmers. It's incredible
OL,16,Fthat our son has done that with his
OL,17,Ffriends."
OL,19,FHe added that he was proud of his
OL,20,Fson's team, labelling them a "very
OL,21,Fspecial group of young men".
